@startuml components
skinparam linetype ortho

title Architecture: The Two-Tiered Universe

package "Layer 2: Higher-Dimensional Logic (Phase Space)" {
    component "The Value (Mono-Type)" as Value
    component "Affine Rotations (Galois Exponentiation)" as Rotations
    
    note right of Value 
      <b>Native System Language</b>
      Lives in GF(257). Knows nothing 
      of English or Pixels.
    end note
    
    note right of Rotations
      <b>Rotation IS Logic</b>
      Generative phase shifts (no XOR here).
      Builds momentum & trajectory.
    end note
    
    Value <-> Rotations : Evolves via f(x) = ax + b (mod 257)
}

package "Layer 1: Static Ground (LSM Storage)" {
    [Morton Key Address Space] as Morton
    component "O(1) Data Retrieval" as Retrieval
    
    note bottom of Morton
      <b>Position IS Data</b>
      X = Byte Value (0-255)
      Y = Sequence Index
      Sequence Index is reset when sequencer makes a new chunk.
      <i>Collision IS Compression</i>
    end note
}

Value --> Morton : Projects Down\n(Coordinate Alignment)
Morton -> Retrieval : Unpack Morton Key\nYields raw Byte to "Puny Humans"

@enduml

